## Welcome to the Guys Afternoon In Page
This is the home page of the Guys Afternoon In team and will be fleshed out with learned lessons as we progress through our skill building process.  

Get your GitHub accounts created dudes and I'll add you on the team. Eventually we will host our repositories on GitHub when we start to/want to work on the same project together.
